    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. A known limitation exists in that the validation dataset covers steady-state operating conditions only and does not include transient start-up or shut-down phases. This limitation is noted and is consistent with standard practice for MRL 2 hemolysis assessments of this device class. The assessment team considers the overall evidence sufficient to support the Accepted decision.",
